(12, '4731944002', '23andMe', 'Head of Design', 'Product', 'Headquarters - Sunnyvale', 'http://platform_1.com/jobs/4731944002', 'http://public-logo.com/23andme', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;23andMe is looking for a design visionary &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;that has a wealth of experience in building world-class product UX, product design and marketing design teams. You have a strong visual aesthetic and an eye for creating world class experiences. You are passionate about health, our consumers, their user perspectives and the brand journey they are on. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;We are looking for an exceptional design leader, thinker and communicator to take the brand and product design to the next level and pioneer uncharted territory. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;You will be responsible for working closely with Product, Insights, Engineering and Marketing to produce a one-of-a kind brand experience - and you excel at building strong cross-functional relationships in a fast-paced organization.&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Youâ€™re an expert at communicating down, up and sideways, so everyone is aware and in sync.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;You will&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt; lead the product and marketing design teams at 23andMe, but ultimately serve the customer. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Your day to day will involve designing amazing user experiences and visuals within the product with the team, but also time spent zooming out to provide big picture design leadership to all design teams. You know how to tell stories, on any platform, that drives engagement. You have a pulse on creative trends in digital marketing and culture and a creative sensibility that extends across content genres. Itâ€™s critical you work closely with our marketing team to help deliver campaigns that effectively support our product launches and site promotions. You have an understanding of how big and little improvements drive a business forward - and you can do more than just come up with big ideas, you know how to get them done.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Who we are&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Since 2006, 23andMeâ€™s mission has been to help people access, understand, and benefit from the human genome. We are a group of passionate individuals pushing the boundaries of whatâ€™s possible to help turn genetic insight into better health and personal understanding.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What youâ€™ll do&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;ul&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Lead 23andMe product and marketing design teams, including UI/UX research, interaction and visual design&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Expand and perfect our in-house design process. As experiences move from requirements to design to execution, we will look to you to ensure our designs meet brand expectations while driving business results. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;You will play a critical role in creating a brand accessible to everyone, and making our product understandable and actionable.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Mentor and grow a talented team of product designers, user researchers, and content strategists to sharpen their craft and deepen their impact. Set clear goals, manage project loads, and ensure high-quality deliverables. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Someone who empowers growth and supports design decisions across all teams.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Champion the consumer. Obsess over the consumer. Empathize with the consumer. You will drive visual and UX design, content strategy and user research across the company in the pursuit of consistent and high quality experiences.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Collaborate cross-functionally with product management, scientists, marketing, engineering to develop and evolve product and marketing research, strategy, roadmap.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;W&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;illing to take risks and push design boundaries - and has a clear POV that can articulate a concept and hold their opinion, while balancing feedback to get to yes/no quickly.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;/ul&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What youâ€™ll bring&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;ul&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;10+ years of experience in design, with 5+ years of experience managing high-performing and creative staff, and 5+ years working collaboratively across engineering, product management and user research teams.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Experience working on end-user facing products and experiences.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Passion to be the voice of design with visibility across our entire organization&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Design leadership experience across the entire product lifecycle managing multiple concurrent projects and budgets.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;User insight and a passion for making peoples&#39; lives better through great product experiences and campaigns.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Excellent communication skills and ability to clearly explain design decisions&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;/ul&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About Us&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;23andMe, Inc. is the leading consumer genetics and research company. Founded in 2006, the mission of the company is to help people access, understand, and benefit from the human genome. The company was named by Glassdoor as one of the Best Places to Work in 2019, MIT Technology Review to its â€œ50 Smartest Companies, 2017â€ list, and named one of Fast Companyâ€™s â€œ25 Brands That Matter Now, 2017â€. 23andMe has millions of customers worldwide, with more than 80 percent of customers consented to participate in research. 23andMe, Inc. is located in Sunnyvale, CA. More information is available at&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.23andme.com/&quot;&gt; &lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;www.23andMe.com&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;At 23andMe, we value a diverse, inclusive workforce and we provide equal employment opportunity for all applicants and employees. All qualified applicants for employment will be considered without regard to an individualâ€™s race, color, sex, gender identity, gender expression, religion, age, national origin or ancestry, citizenship, physical or mental disability, medical condition, family care status, marital status, domestic partner status, sexual orientation, genetic information, military or veteran status, or any other basis protected by federal, state or local laws.&amp;nbsp; If you are unable to submit your application because of incompatible assistive technology or a disability, please contact us at accommodations-ext@23andme.com. 23andMe will reasonably accommodate qualified individuals with disabilities to the extent required by applicable law.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Please note: 23andMe does not accept agency resumes and we are not responsible for any fees related to unsolicited resumes. Thank you.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', '2020-08-04 13:15:09'),
(13, '4710347002', '23andMe', 'Patent Agent', 'Legal and Regulatory Affairs', 'South San Francisco, California', 'http://platform_1.com/jobs/4710347002', 'http://public-logo.com/23andme', '&lt;div&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;23andMe is seeking a highly motivated, experienced Patent Agent to join the legal department to implement and develop strategy and protection of intellectual property related to 23andMeâ€™s large and small molecule therapeutic programs and Personal Genome Services. You are adept at providing relevant and clear guidance, including patentability, freedom-to-operate, infringement and validity analyses, and risk evaluation and mitigation strategies to scientists and business leaders in support of business objectives and decision-making.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;In addition to your patent agent work, you will also perform general duties of a patent and trademark paralegal. You are exceedingly well-organized, flexible and enjoy challenges of working on diverse issues daily. You are a collaborative partner, work rapidly, diligently and independently with minimal direction.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;strong&gt;Who we are&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;div&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;Since 2006, 23andMeâ€™s mission has been to help people access, understand, and benefit from the human genome. We are a group of passionate individuals pushing the boundaries of whatâ€™s possible to help turn genetic insight into better health and personal understanding.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you&#39;ll do&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;ul&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Perform global patent preparation and prosecution, portfolio development and management, patent searching and/or landscaping, patent diligence assessments, freedom-to-operate, infringement and validity analyses, and risk evaluation and mitigation strategies&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Advise the business stakeholders on patent strategies, risk, and associated mitigation strategies&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Manages external relationships with outside counsel and collaborators&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Act as a key resource for outside patent counsel and patent vendors, while managing coordination and communication with internal business stakeholders&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Lead development and implementation of patent operational processes, as needed, such as patent formalities and official inventor Declarations and Assignments&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Monitor timelines to ensure timely execution of patent deadlines&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;/ul&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you&#39;ll bring&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;ul&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Admission to practice before United States Patent and Trademark Office (required)&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;5+ years of experience practicing large molecule patent law (required)&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Experience in all aspects of U.S. and foreign intellectual property law relating to biotechnology, in the pharmaceutical industry with a law firm or corporation&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Undergraduate and masters or advanced degree in biology or biochemistry (required)&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Expert analytical, legal drafting and verbal and written communication skills and the ability to effectively communicate with business stakeholders across the organization&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Strong counseling skills with a client service focus, keen attention to detail and the ability to work independently and in teams; strong organizational skills; the ability to prioritize, work efficiently or multi-task, and to be agile and meet aggressive deadlines&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;/ul&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About Us&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;23andMe, Inc. is the leading consumer genetics and research company. Founded in 2006, the mission of the company is to help people access, understand, and benefit from the human 