their business, and what 6sense means to their success&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Collaborate and win as a team â€“ Youâ€™ll compete, but above that youâ€™ll collaborate, youâ€™ll share what is working, youâ€™ll help the team win, youâ€™ll take on projects outside of closing deals.&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;/ul&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.linkedin.com/pulse/20m-day-6sense-changing-game-b2b-marketing-sales-amanda-kahlow&quot;&gt;We are creating a different kind of company&lt;/a&gt;.&amp;nbsp; If this sounds like a breath of fresh air and a place where youâ€™ll thrive as you take your success to the next level, we should talk!&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Minimum Requirements:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;ul&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Bachelor&#39;s degree from an accredited University is strongly preferred&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;2-4 Years of full-time corporate sales experience (Marketing Tech/Software sales is a plus)&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;6 Months of corporate prospecting experience&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;/ul&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Preferred Requirements:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;ul&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Understanding of B2B Enterprise Marketing &amp;amp; Sales&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Inside sales experience a plus&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Enterprise prospecting experience a plus&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Excellent written/verbal communication skills&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Strong problem solving skills&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Motivation, drive and a self-starting attitude&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Ability to work in a fast paced, team environment&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Ability to understand customer needs and meet that need with a successful product sale&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Good time management with strong organizational skills&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;/ul&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Location&lt;/strong&gt;: New York City&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;/div&gt;', '2020-07-29 12:18:51'),
