(72, '4792486002', '98point6', 'Senior Engineering Manager', 'Engineering', 'Seattle HQ', 'http://platform_1.com/jobs/4792486002', 'http://public-logo.com/98point6', '&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Our mission is to deliver high-quality primary care that is accessible, convenient and affordable for all. Every single day youâ€™ll be working on challenging problems with an exceptional team to profoundly transform primary care and improve peopleâ€™s quality of life.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;div&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Commercial Squad&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;div&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;Squads at 98point6 consist of a cross-functional team of engineers, one or more product managers and an engineering manager. The Commercial squad owns feature areas associated with our customers that are not direct-to-consumer, such as self-insured employers and universities. Feature areas include onboarding, subscriptions, payments, patient attribution and eligibility processing.&lt;strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;div&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Your role and impact&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;As an engineering manager, you will be responsible for leading a team to deliver new product features and improvements, as well as driving efficiency, operational excellence and quality. You will collaborate with a product manager to support company goals, identify and prioritize the work for the team and understand and negotiate requirements from third parties and external clients. You will be responsible for hiring and developing talent on the team and ensuring each member grows both technically and professionally.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;div&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/