(85, '4213264002', 'Abstract', 'Senior Software Engineer, Infrastructure', 'Engineering', 'Remote, United States', 'http://platform_1.com/jobs/4213264002', 'http://public-logo.com/abstract', '&lt;div&gt;\n&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the Role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\n&lt;div&gt;&lt;span class=&quot; author-d-1gg9uz65z1iz85zgdz68zmqkz84zo2qoxwekncz82zp33z74zz84z1z89zz83zz75zjz88z4dz74z6yz65zihkdh8hz69z&quot;&gt;We are&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot; author-d-iz88z86z86za0dz67zz78zz78zz74zz68zjz80zz71z9iz90z95lz88znz68z5z79z72z75zcz85zz77zjz82zz81z1z75zz70zz87zw1z83z7z69zz76zz70z7d8&quot;&gt; looking for engineers to help us grow our systems infrastructure. At Abstract we develop desktop and web applications that help teams design with confidence by providing a version control system and collaboration platform focused on design artifacts.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;div&gt;&lt;span class=&quot; author-d-iz88z86z86za0dz67zz78zz78zz74zz68zjz80zz71z9iz90z95lz88znz68z5z79z72z75zcz85zz77zjz82zz81z1z75zz70zz87zw1z83z7z69zz76zz70z7d8&quot;&gt;As a&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot; author-d-1gg9uz65z1iz85zgdz68zmqkz84zo2qovvlngz88zz65zz78zz85z9sz75z7nz81zz69zz76zz80zsnz82z08bz88zz65zl0uk8z66z&quot;&gt;n operations&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot; author-d-iz88z86z86za0dz67zz78zz78zz74zz68zjz80zz71z9iz90z9fnz72zz73zz79zxlz68z43oz75zacq2n3vz79zz85zz89zj15z83zz77z7z71zz72z&quot;&gt;/infrastructure&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot; author-d-iz88z86z86za0dz67zz78zz78zz74zz68zjz80zz71z9iz90z95lz88znz68z5z79z72z75zcz85zz77zjz82zz81z1z75zz70zz87zw1z83z7z69zz76zz70z7d8&quot;&gt; team, we&#39;re firm believers in managing our infrastructure with code, reviewing each other&#39;s work, and striving to provide a great experience to both our customers and the rest of the Abstract engineering team.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot; author-d-1gg9uz65z1iz85zgdz68zmqkz84zo2qovvlngz88zz65zz78zz85z9sz75z7nz81zz69zz76zz80zsnz82z08bz88zz65zl0uk8z66z&quot;