pon hire. Applicants must be currently authorized to work in the United States on a full-time basis; Elastic Projects will not sponsor applicants for work visas.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;div&gt;&lt;span class=&quot; author-d-iz88z86z86za0dz67zz78zz78zz74zz68zjz80zz71z9iz90z95lz88znz68z5z79z72z75zcz85zz77zjz82zz81z1z75zz70zz87zw1z83z7z69zz76zz70z7d8&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;div&gt;&lt;span class=&quot; author-d-iz88z86z86za0dz67zz78zz78zz74zz68zjz80zz71z9iz90z95lz88znz68z5z79z72z75zcz85zz77zjz82zz81z1z75zz70zz87zw1z83z7z69zz76zz70z7d8&quot;&gt;As part of our security protocols, offers are contingent on successful completion of a background check.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;/div&gt;', '2020-07-30 16:01:19'),
(86, '4819268002', 'Abstract', 'Solutions Engineer', 'Sales', 'Remote, United States', 'http://platform_1.com/jobs/4819268002', 'http://public-logo.com/abstract', '&lt;h3&gt;About the Role:&lt;/h3&gt;\n&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;The Solutions Engineering team plays a key role in setting Abstract customers up for success. As a Solutions Engineer, you will work hand-in-hand with Design leaders at some of the worldâ€™s largest enterprise companies to get their teams up and running with Abstract. You will work alongside our Account Executives and Account Managers; develop custom team workflows, strategies, and configurations; and use your experience and ingenuity to implement Abstract alongside customersâ€™ existing suite of software tools.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;h3&gt;What you&#39;ll do:&lt;/h3&gt;\n&lt;ul&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Provide technical assistance and consultations during pre-sales and customer trial periods&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Work with Abstract customers to set up their accounts to optimize their workflows with Abstract alongside their other software tools&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Teach early Abstract adopters how the product works, from introductory overviews and best practices to deep dives into customer-specific workflows&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Partner with Account Executives and Account Managers to develop and implement sales and expansion strategies for the adoption of Abstract at enterprise companies&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Match customer needs with product capabilities&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Collect and report user feedback and feature requests&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;/ul&gt;\n&lt;h3&gt;What you&#39;ll bring:&lt;/h3&gt;\n&lt;ul&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Knowledge of the design software ecosystem&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Experience implementing software at large enterprise organizations&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Experience working cross-functionally with Design, Engineering, and Sales&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Exceptional problem solving skills: demonstrated ability to structure complex problems and develop solutions&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Ability to work independently in a fast-paced environment with minimal supervision&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;/ul&gt;\n&lt;h3&gt;Bonus if you have:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/h3&gt;\n&lt;ul&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Familiarity with different design team practices, workflows, and tools&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Familiarity working with Abstract, Sketch, and/or Adobe XD&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Experience with SSO configurations&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Experience working with A