(116, '2124214', 'Acquia', 'Principal Software Engineer - PHP', 'Engineering', 'Boston, MA, United States', 'http://platform_1.com/jobs/2124214', 'http://public-logo.com/acquia', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Acquia is the open source digital experience company. We provide the world&#39;s most ambitious brands with technology that allows them to embrace innovation and create customer moments that matter. At Acquia we believe in the power of community and collaboration - giving our customers the freedom to build tomorrow on their terms.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Headquartered in Boston, we have been named as one of North Americaâ€™s fastest growing software companies as reported by Deloitte and Inc. Magazine, and have been rated a leader by the analyst community and named one of the Best Places to Work by the Boston Business Journal. We are Acquia. We are building for the future of the web, and we want you to be a part of it.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the team you will be onâ€¦&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;The Principal Software Engineer is an integral member of the &lt;/span&gt;Acquia technology team&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt; and ensures that the companyâ€™s software products are well engineered, operable, maintainable, and aligned with the strategy and vision of the business.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;We work on a variety of exciting projects ranging from running massive microservice infrastructures, building highly available database clusters, scaling data pipelines and machine learning to enable our customers to deliver amazing digital experiences that are visited by millions of people each day.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;As the Principal Software Engineer, you willâ€¦&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;ul&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Mentor and lead engineering teams via quality of ideas, code and communication as a domain expert&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Influence internal stakeholders, including the CPO and CTO, engineering leads, product managers, and executives&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Diagram and document current and future architectural plans that technical and non-technical stakeholders can understand how Acquia&#39;s technology works&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Drive deployment of new features or systems and the retirement of old ones, and be a change advocate for customers and employees, in order to simplify product development and operations and increase velocity&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Write blogs, white papers, and demonstrate domain expertise for internal/external publication&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Collaborate with vendors and influence their roadmap to align with Acquiaâ€™s long term roadmap&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;/ul&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Youâ€™ll enjoy this role if you areâ€¦&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;ul&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Able to lead by example&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;A passionate learner who provides guidance through questions as opposed to statements&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Inclined to document and diagram ideas as a primary method of communication&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Able to communicate complex, technical concepts to a wide range of stakeholders with varying perspectives and technical expertise&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Comfortable under pressure and welcomes new challenges&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Able to work in an agile DevOps methodology collaborating and enabling all around them&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;/ul&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What youâ€™ll need to be successfulâ€¦&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;ul&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Deep, working knowledge of AWS C&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;loud hosting experience, Ruby&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Strong Object Oriented Programming experience in PHP&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Holistic understanding of the Internet and hosting from the network layer up through the application layer&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Strong background with service oriented architectures, and building scalable, reliable systems&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;/ul&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Extra credit if you have...&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;ul&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Strong experience in different programming languages: Go, Python, Varnish, CDN&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Configuration management (e.g., Puppet, Ansible, Chef)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Experience with modern containerization systems: Docker, LXC, etc.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Web security and compliance experience (e.g., Firewalls, IDS/IPS systems, DOS prevention and PCI, HIPAA, FedRAMP, etc.)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Networking (e.g., TCP/IP, Routing, DNS, load balancing, HTTP caching, clustering, VPN, etc.)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Experienced Linux OS system management (Ubuntu, Centos)&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Automated testing and continuous integration experience--Jenkins, TravisCI, unit tests, system tests, etc.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Drupal setup, maintenance and operational knowledge&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Advanced knowledge of distributed database and file system management and concepts&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;/ul&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;We are committed to continually strengthening our people-first culture within our Acquia family. Acquia is an equal opportunity employer committed to fostering a diverse and inclusive environment for all. Our highly motivated team features individuals from a multitude of backgrounds who offer their unique perspectives, starting with their first project as a new hire to their 100th as a manager and beyond. For every step in between, we help Acquians grow by promoting a culture of continuous learning through mentorship, knowledge-sharing, feedback, and more.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Thank you for considering Acquia for your next career move, and we look forward to receiving your application. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Thereâ€™s no such thing as the perfect candidate. &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;So, weâ€™re not looking for someone who matches all of our criteria; weâ€™re looking for someone with the potential to grow outward and upward. Regardless of how much of the criteria you meet, you should apply!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.acquia.com/&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Acquia&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt; is an equal opportunity (EEO) employer. We hire without regard to age, color, disability, gender (including gender identity), marital status, national origin, race, religion, sex, sexual orientation, veteran status, or any other status protected by applicable law.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;', '2020-08-05 21:18:54'),
(117, '2163420', 'Acquia', 'Principal Software Engineer (PHP + Symfony/Laravel/Codeigniter + MySQL)', 'Engineering', 'Pune, India', 'http://platform_1.com/jobs/2163420', 'http://public-logo.com/acquia', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Location: &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Pune, India&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Role: &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Principal Software Engineer&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About Acquiaâ€¦&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Freedom. For tens of thousands of high-profile sites around the world and the users that depend on them, Acquia means freedom. Our purpose is to deliver the highest performance platform for Drupal-powered sites and back that up with the best support available anywhere. With Drupal and Acquia you are free to create and express yourself knowing that no matter how big your ideas become we&#39;ve got your back.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;The Acquia Cloud Site Factory team is growing to meet increasing customer demand for flexible site management at scale. In this role your expertise and craftsmanship will shape the next phase of development in high-scale many-site management. If you are interested in working on ambitious technical challenges and are compelled to take your skills to the next level on a product that is critical to Acquia&#39;s success, this is your opportunity.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;As the Principal Software Engineer, you willâ€¦&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;ul&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Participate in short daily stand-up meetings&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Work with talented and thoughtful engineers&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Design, implement, and operate the services you develop&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Research and define future work to delight high-profile customers&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Collaborate with other product teams on cross-functional projects&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Review code and coach junior team members&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;/ul&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Youâ€™ll enjoy this role if youâ€¦&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;ul&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Curiosity and a passion to create&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Strong software development and technical leadership skills&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Expert level knowledge and experience working with PHP&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Full stack development experience using Linux, Apache, and MySQL&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;BS in Computer Science or 8+ years equivalent experience&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Ability to develop beautiful, secure, high performance code&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Excellent organizational and communication skills, both verbal and written&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Ability to absorb complex ideas and explain them concisely&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Ability to work well both independently and in a team setting&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;/ul&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Extra credit if youâ€¦&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;ul&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Drupal development experience&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Large scale task automation&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Linux / Unix system administration&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Languages: PHP, Ruby, Go&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Automated testing experience: Jenkins, TravisCI, unit tests, system tests, etc.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Amazon Web Services experience&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Other cloud hosting experience (e.g. Google Compute, Azure)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Open source development and contribution&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Agile development (scrum)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Containerization using Docker&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;/ul&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.acquia.com/&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Acquia&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt; is an equal opportunity (EEO) employer. We hire without regard to age, color, disability, gender (including gender identity), marital status, national origin, race, religion, sex, sexual orientation, veteran status, or any other status protected by applicable law.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', '2020-08-05 21:18:54'),
(118, '2163491', 'Acquia', 'Principal Software Engineer (Ruby + AWS)', 'Engineering', 'Pune, India', 'http://platform_1.com/jobs/2163491', 'http://public-logo.com/acquia', '&lt;p&gt;Acquia is driving the open-source revolution as the leading provider of cloud-based digital experience management solutions. What does that mean? Collaborators within Acquia and volunteers around the globe are continually strengthening Drupal, our award-winning platform, to fuel the dreamers and doers who are delivering amazing digital experiences at the worldâ€™s&amp;nbsp; most ambitious brands like Pinterest, Whole Foods, and the Australian government. Our success begins with our team. Thatâ€™s why Acquia prides itself on hiring innovative people who demonstrate an eagerness to grow, make an impact, and seek out new challenges to create bigger, better, and bolder customer experiences. To do this, we match our talented new hires that have a passion and dedication to learning and contributing with opportunities that not only harness their strengths but also challenge them to&lt;br&gt;stretch beyond their comfort zone and tackle problems at the edge of their skill set. Our goal is to present opportunities that inspire collaboration, creativity, and professional development.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;About the team you will be onâ€¦&lt;br&gt;The Principal Software Engineer is an integral member of the Cloud Data Services Team and ensures that the companyâ€™s software products are well engineered, operable, maintainable, and aligned with the strategy and vision of the business.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;The Acquia Cloud Data services team is growing rapidly and we are looking for passionate software engineers who want to collaborate, define, design, build, and operate enterprise-level persistent cloud services. This fast-paced team is focused on creating scalable Database and&lt;br&gt;File System services and features from the ground up that are the backbone enabling our customers to securely deliver their brands and digital experience across the world to millions of users.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;As the Principal Software Engineer, you willâ€¦&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;ul&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Influence and lead other product and engineering teams via quality of ideas, code and communication as a domain expert but not as the reporting manager for any of them&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Interface with and influence internal stakeholders, including the CPO and CTO, engineering leads, product managers, and executives&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Diagram and document current and future architectural plans sufficiently that necessary stakeholders can understand how Acquia&amp;amp;#39;s technology works&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Drive deployment of new features or systems and the retirement of old ones, overcoming inertial resistance to change from customers and employees, in order to simplify product development and operations and increase velocity&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Have a solid understanding of the platform and how different parts interact with each other&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Mentor other engineers&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Write blogs, white papers, and demonstrate domain expertise for internal/external publication&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with vendors and influence their roadmap to align with Acquiaâ€™s long term roadmap&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;/ul&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;Youâ€™ll enjoy this role if you areâ€¦&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;ul&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Able to influence and lead experienced and battle-tested engineers by example&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;A passionate learner who provides guidance through questions as opposed to statements&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Inclined to document and diagram ideas as a primary method of communication&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Able to communicate complex, technical concepts to a wide range of stakeholders with varying perspectives and technical expertise&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Comfortable under pressure and welcome new challenges&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Able to work in an agile DevOps methodology collaborating and enabling all around the&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;/ul&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;What youâ€™ll need to be successfulâ€¦&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;ul&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;10+ years of related experience&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Strong working knowledge of LAMP and Ruby based stacks&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Strong Object Oriented Programming experience&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Vast Amazon Web Services experience&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Holistic understanding of the Internet and hosting from the network layer up through the application layer.&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Strong background with service oriented architecture, building scalable, reliable systems&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;\n&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;Extra credit if you have...&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;ul&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Strong experience in different programming languages: PHP, Ruby, Go, Python&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Configuration management (e.g., Puppet, Ansible, Chef)&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Web security and compliance experience (e.g., Firewalls, IDS/IPS systems, DOS prevention and PCI, HIPAA, FedRAMP, etc.)&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Networking (e.g., TCP/IP, Routing, DNS, load balancing, HTTP caching, clustering,&lt;br&gt;VPN, etc.)&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Experience with modern containerization systems&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Docker, LXC, runc, etc.&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Experience with MySQL&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Experience with Kubernetes&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Linux OS system management&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Ubuntu, RHEL, Amazon Linux, etc.&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Operational knowledge of Drupal in a production setting&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Advanced knowledge of distributed database management and concepts&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Advanced knowledge of distributed file system management and concepts&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;/ul&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;We are committed to continually strengthening our people-first culture within our Acquia family. Acquia is an equal opportunity employer committed to fostering a diverse and inclusive environment for all. Our highly motivated team features individuals from a multitude of backgrounds who offer their unique perspectives, starting with their first project as a new hire to their 100th as a manager and beyond. For every step in between, we help Acquians grow by promoting a culture of continuous learning through mentorship, knowledge-sharing, feedback, and more. Acquia is an equal opportunity (EEO) employer. We hire without regard to age, color, disability, gender (including gender identity), marital status, national origin, race, religion, sex, sexual orientation, veteran status, or any other status protected by applicable law.&lt;/p&gt;', '2020-08-07 08:35:49'),
(119, '2204160', 'Acquia', 'Product Manager (Data Science)', 'Products', 'Pune, India', 'http://platform_1.com/jobs/2204160', 'http://public-logo.com/acquia', '&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Product Manager (Marketing Cloud, Machine Learning)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Acquia is the open source digital experience company. We provide the world&#39;s most ambitious brands with technology that allows them to embrace innovation and create customer moments that matter. At Acquia we believe in the power of community and collaboration - giving our customers the freedom to build tomorrow on their terms.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Headquartered in Boston, we have been named as one of North Americaâ€™s fastest growing software companies as reported by Deloitte and Inc. Magazine, and have been rated a leader by the analyst community and named one of the Best Places to Work by the Boston Business Journal. We are Acquia. We are building for the future, and we want you to be a part of it.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the team you will be onâ€¦&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Acquia Marketing Cloud is the open marketing cloud and is purpose-built as a SaaS solution that enables cross-channel marketing, and scales across brands. The Acquia marketing cloud product portfolio includes AgilOne, the premier Customer Data Platform, Lift web personalization solution and Mautic marketing automation solution.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.acquia.com/products-services/acquia-agilone&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Acquia AgilOne&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt; is the leading Customer Data Platform for enterprise B2C companies. AgilOneâ€™s vision is to restore the personal relationships companies once had with customers before channel-specific marketing silos got in the way. AgilOne enables a single customer view through a best of breed identity resolution engine used on first party customer data. Machine learning and analytical algorithms enhance customer data leveraged through real-time APIs and orchestrated across all touchpoints. AgilOne helps brands build authentic omni-channel customer relationships that maximize lifetime value. AgilOne supports more than 150 brands worldwide, including lululemon, Hugo Boss and Schwanâ€™s.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;As a Product Manager, you willâ€¦&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;ul&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Work closely with our machine learning team in managing projects and product roadmap&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Coordinate with our OEM partnerâ€™s roadmap and prioritizing requirements, and executing the plan with the partner and internal stakeholders&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Define how users of Acquia Marketing Cloud can better visualize and leverage machine learning in our entire Marketing Cloud product suite&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Work closely with our product marketing team to evangelize our Machine Learning capabilities both internally and externally&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Deeply know the problems youâ€™re tackling through regular interaction with customers, and various internal teams such as customer success, implementation, support, solutions engineering and sales.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;/ul&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Youâ€™ll enjoy this role ifâ€¦&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;ul&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;You have technical knowledge in Machine Learning that enables you to understand problems and scope features.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;You are curious and scrappy, and are able to thrive in a dynamic, ambiguous environment.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;You are an extremely strong and effective communicator across a range of situations. From pitching our leadership team, prospects or customers on our roadmap, to digging into a feature with your team.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;You flourish when it comes to cross-functional teamwork working with globally distributed teams&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;/ul&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What youâ€™ll need to be successfulâ€¦&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;ul&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;5+ years of relevant experience in product management delivering enterprise solutions&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Knowledge of marketing, analytics and data science and familiarity with marketing technology&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Great knowledge of Machine Learning concepts and use cases&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Solid understanding of SQL, big data and APIs.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Strong analytical and critical problem solving skills with high attention to detail.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Familiarity with marketing technology, and knowledge of analytics and data science functions.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Proactive, independent thinker with high energy and entrepreneurial mindset.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Exceptional verbal, written and interpersonal communications skills for both technical and non-technical audiences.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Experience working with engineering teams using Agile/Scrum methodologies.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Bachelorâ€™s degree in Computer Science, Electrical Engineering or similar quantitative field.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;/ul&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Extra credit if you haveâ€¦&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;ul&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Experience with data science tools or marketing tools leveraging data science&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Experience with key Product Management functions, including writing requirements, creating wireframes, market research, competitive analysis, product planning and reporting.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Experience with MarTech or AdTech products.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Experience working with global teams.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Experience building or working with personalization technologies&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Have experience leading integrations across multiple products including acquired products&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;/ul&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;We are committed to continually strengthening our people-first culture within our Acquia family. Acquia is an equal opportunity employer committed to fostering a diverse and inclusive environment for all. Our highly motivated team features individuals from a multitude of backgrounds who offer their unique perspectives, starting with their first project as a new hire to their 100th as a manager and beyond. For every step in between, we help Acquians grow by promoting a culture of continuous learning through mentorship, knowledge-sharing, feedback, and more.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Thank you for considering Acquia for your next career move, and we look forward to receiving your application. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Thereâ€™s no such thing as the perfect candidate. &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;So, weâ€™re not looking for someone who matches all of our criteria; weâ€™re looking for someone with the potential to grow outward and upward.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', '2020-08-07 23:19:18'),
(120, '2242771', 'Acquia', 'Project Manager, PS', 'Customer Success', 'Pune, India', 'http://platform_1.com/jobs/2242771', 'http://public-logo.com/acquia', '&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Job description&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;\n&lt;h1&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Project Manager&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Team&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;: Delivery&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Direct reports&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;: No&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Summary:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt; A Project Manager is a member of the Professional Services delivery team that builds and maintains applications on the Acquia Platform on behalf of customers and partners. A Project Manager is responsible for executing a project according to Acquiaâ€™s methodology.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Key responsibilities:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;ul&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Accountable for delivering successful customer projects using Acquiaâ€™s agile development methodology&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Accountable for managing change in order to meet or exceeding project goals, including budget, scope, and timeline goals&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Accountable for accurately communicating project status internally and to customers&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Accountable for providing informed and timely planning, requirements management, and training support to customers&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Accountable for project compliance with Acquia processes and methodologies&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Accountable for continuous improvement of the project management discipline in Acquiaâ€™s Professional Services&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Ad Hoc duties as assigned&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;/ul&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Key requirements:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;ul&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Experience in project management role within a digital/IT organization&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;ul&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Hiring guidelines: 5+ years for PM, 10+ years for Sr., 15+ years for principal&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;/ul&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Project Management and/or SCRUM certification desirable&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Direct experience in a client service role&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Superior understanding of content management systems, Drupal strongly preferred&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Excellent written and verbal communication skills&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;/ul&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Skills and Qualifications:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;table&gt;\n&lt;tbody&gt;\n&lt;tr&gt;\n&lt;td&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Project Manager&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;/td&gt;\n&lt;td&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Senior Project Manager&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;/td&gt;\n&lt;td&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Principal Project Manager&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;/td&gt;\n&lt;/tr&gt;\n&lt;tr&gt;\n&lt;td&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Problem Solving&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Develops elegant solutions to complex problems.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;br&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Break down a problem into discrete, actionable items; identify risks; and note assumptions.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;br&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Extreme attention to detail, ability to focus (you and others) and eliminate distractions&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;br&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Communication&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Communicates honestly, openly, with transparency.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;br&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Displays empathy, patience and emotional IQ with customers&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;br&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;When necessary, acknowledges personal limitations (personal capabilities, time, etc.)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;br&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Self Direction&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Passion for learning and discovery. Self direction. When you don&#39;t know an answer, you go find it.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;br&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Participates in knowledge sharing activities&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;/td&gt;\n&lt;td&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;In addition to capabilities of a Project Manager:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;br&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Problem Solving&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Can handle ambiguity. Identify the challenges that prevent progress. Can bring order to the challenges.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;br&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Anticipate challenges.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;br&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Communication&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Delivers hard messages (with appropriate wording, tact, â€¦); Fact-based communication; Handles pressure; Messaging in appropriate context.&amp;nbsp; Provide background, connect to the big picture.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;br&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Matches the most effective medium to the delivery of a message. Uses visual aids, in-person communications, etc.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;br&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Leadership&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Willing to take responsibility and ownership&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;br&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Creates and identifies opportunities for knowledge and asset creation to further the capabilities and skillsets of others&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;br&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Problem Solving&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Develops elegant solutions to complex problems&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;br&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Handles pressure gracefully.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;br&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Makes risk-based decisions and holds team and self accountable&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;br&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Communication&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Communicates complex ideas in easy to understand ways. Able to make connections between new, complex concepts and familiar, shared experiences. Able to connect the dots.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;br&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Able to perceive project and organizational issues quickly through effective questioning&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;br&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Leadership&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Recognized expertise and able to effectively communicate with others in specific areas of focus.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;br&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Sets aside personal ego in favor of success&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;br&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Defines clear expectations for self and colleagues&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;br&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Sees qualities in others and enhances them&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;br&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Able to empower others in order to scale an effort&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;/td&gt;\n&lt;td&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;In addition to capabilities of a Sr. Project Manager:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;br&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Problem Solving&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Develops elegant solutions to complex problems&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;br&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Handles pressure gracefully.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;br&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Communication&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Communicates complex ideas in easy to understand ways. Able to make connections between new, complex concepts and familiar, shared experiences. Able to connect the dots.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;br&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Possesses a strong executive presence with the ability to establish credibility in the first client meeting&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;br&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Leadership&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Recognized expertise and able to effectively communicate with others in specific areas of focus.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;br&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Builds and adapts project management framework to address change&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;br&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Sets aside personal ego in favor of success&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;br&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Possesses a philosophy of coaching&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;/td&gt;\n&lt;/tr&gt;\n&lt;/tbody&gt;\n&lt;/table&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://docs.google.com/document/d/1iJQ2NoTchZb7X1R5UEgW-qB4Sku2fUGl_AD6LvJdEO0/edit&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Professional Services Job Descriptions&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://docs.google.com/document/d/1kR4_Ri8wMk2xut0--Fa8u-XSK9yxgpAEB6_yR2lk3ns/edit&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Sapient Program Manager JD&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Interview Process:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;table&gt;\n&lt;tbody&gt;\n&lt;tr&gt;\n&lt;td&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Interview stages&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;/td&gt;\n&lt;td&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Categories /skills to be assessed&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;/td&gt;\n&lt;td&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Interviewer&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;/td&gt;\n&lt;/tr&gt;\n&lt;tr&gt;\n&lt;td&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Recruiter Screening&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;/td&gt;\n&lt;td&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/td&gt;\n&lt;td&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/td&gt;\n&lt;/tr&gt;\n&lt;tr&gt;\n&lt;td&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Engagement&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;/td&gt;\n&lt;td&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/td&gt;\n&lt;td&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/td&gt;\n&lt;/tr&gt;\n&lt;tr&gt;\n&lt;td&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;First Interview&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;/td&gt;\n&lt;td&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/td&gt;\n&lt;td&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/td&gt;\n&lt;/tr&gt;\n&lt;tr&gt;\n&lt;td&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Second Interview&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;/td&gt;\n&lt;td&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/td&gt;\n&lt;td&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/td&gt;\n&lt;/tr&gt;\n&lt;tr&gt;\n&lt;td&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Third Interview&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;/td&gt;\n&lt;td&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/td&gt;\n&lt;td&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/td&gt;\n&lt;/tr&gt;\n&lt;/tbody&gt;\n&lt;/table&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://docs.google.com/document/d/1dQ7G9c7iqu1XFEAkIGFj35hesWqw4QKjAtS-kkcmxvA/edit&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Acquia PM Case Study&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', '2020-08-05 21:18:54');
