&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;The Senior Software Engineer is an integral member of the &lt;/span&gt;Acquia technology team&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt; and ensures that the companyâ€™s software products are well engineered, operable, maintainable, and aligned with the strategy and vision of the business.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;We work on a variety of exciting projects ranging from running massive microservice infrastructures, building highly available database clusters, scaling data pipelines and machine learning to enable our customers to deliver amazing digital experiences that are visited by millions of people each day.&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;h3&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;As the Senior Software Engineer, you willâ€¦&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\n&lt;ul&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Design and develop features for a distributed, multi-tenant, and scale out edge, routing, and web caching platform services&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Work in a DevOps focused team owning and operating the services you build in accordance with service level objectives.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Build high volume, highly available services in PHP and Ruby utilizing the latest cloud based services from Amazon Web Services.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Working in an Agile Scrum team building shippable product increments that meet the goals set by the Product Owners.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Develop unit and automated integration tests that give the team confidence to deploy to production on a predictable cadence.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Participate in the entire software development lifecycle including development, automated test construction, deployment and operations.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Be an active participant in Scrum ceremonies.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Provide product support to internal and external stakeholders.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;/ul&gt;\n&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Youâ€™ll enjoy this role if you areâ€¦&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\n&lt;ul&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Executes projects effectively and efficiently as a leader on teams&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Uses sound rationale for problem identification and decision-making, and can transfer that knowledge to more junior engineers&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Works in a collaborative and supportive manner with not only his team but internal stakeholders as well.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Strives to consistently achieve excellence in work delivered not only for themselves, but for their teammates.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Passionate about creating and maintaining high quality software with test-driven development, continuous refactoring and an eye for simplicity.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Experienced in multiple programming languages, including PHP, Ruby and Rust.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Very comfortable in a Linux environment, including low-level networking fundamentals like ARP, DHCP, TCP/IP, DNS, routing, iptables, etc.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Firsthand experience in designing and implementing multiple scalable network solutions using open source tech like NGINX, Varnish, Istio, etc in public and private cloud environments including AWS, GCP, Bluemix, etc.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Relevant technical degree or 5+ years equivalent experience&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;/ul&gt;\n&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What youâ€™ll need to be successfulâ€¦&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\n&lt;ul&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Deep, working knowledge of LAMP stack&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;PHP and Ruby knowledge&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Cloud hosting experience&amp;nbsp; (e.g., Amazon Web Services, Google Compute)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Holistic understanding of the Internet and hosting from the network layer up through the application layer.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;5+ years of related experience&